 information with sellers",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content3:"We accept the following payment methods:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content4:"Security certifications:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content1:"We are committed to protecting your privacy. Multiple safeguards secure your data, and we will never share or sell your information without your consent.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content2:"View TikTok Shop's <link>Privacy Policy</link> to understand your rights, data security methods, and use of any information.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content3:"Need help? Our virtual help center is available within the TikTok app 24/7, and our live agents are ready to assist you during business hours.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_learn_more:"Learn more",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_money_back_guarantee_content:"Our coverage is completely free and automatic on eligible orders for up to 90 days - if your item arrives damaged or defective. Limitations and exclusions apply.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_secure_payments_content5:"To use any of the payment options below, please make your purchase in-app:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_subtitle:"We're committed to giving you a great shopping experience.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle1:"Secure payments",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle2:"Money-back guarantee",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle4:"24/7 in-app support",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_subtitle5:"Data privacy",tts_shop_purchase_protections_module_title:"TikTok Shop protections",tts_shop_web_promotion_tiktok_picks:"TikTok Picks",tts_web_seo_coupon_center_title:"Coupon center",ug_paid_ads_seo_Shop_BR:"TikTok Shop Brazil",ug_paid_ads_seo_Shop_MX:"TikTok Shop M\xe9xico",ug_paid_ads_seo_Shop_Tokopedia:"Shop | Tokopedia",ug_paid_ads_seo_TikTok_Shop_Malaysia:"TikT