_refunds_content4:"Ho\xe0n ti\u1EC1n t\u1EE9c th\xec t\u1EA1i b\u01B0u c\u1EE5c cho \u0111\u01A1n \u0111\u1EE7 \u0111i\u1EC1u ki\u1EC7n tr\u1EA3 h\xe0ng",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content1:"TikTok Shop s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng ph\u01B0\u01A1ng th\u1EE9c thanh to\xe1n b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt cao. C\xe1c giao d\u1ECBch \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c m\xe3 h\xf3a ho\xe0n to\xe0n v\xe0 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c quy \u0111\u1ECBnh b\u1EDFi Ti\xeau chu\u1EA9n b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt d\u1EEF li\u1EC7u ng\xe0nh th\u1EBB thanh to\xe1n (PCI DSS)",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content2:"Ch\xfang t\xf4i kh\xf4ng bao gi\u1EDD chia s\u1EBB th\xf4ng tin thanh to\xe1n v\u1EDBi ng\u01B0\u1EDDi b\xe1n ",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content3:"Ch\xfang t\xf4i ch\u1EA5p nh\u1EADn c\xe1c ph\u01B0\u01A1ng th\u1EE9c thanh to\xe1n sau:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_Secure_Payments_content4:"Ch\u1EE9ng nh\u1EADn b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt:",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content1:"Ch\xfang t\xf4i cam k\u1EBFt b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 quy\u1EC1n ri\xeang t\u01B0 c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n. Ch\xfang t\xf4i c\xf3 nhi\u1EC1u bi\u1EC7n ph\xe1p b\u1EA3o v\u1EC7 b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt d\u1EEF li\u1EC7u c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n v\xe0 ch\xfang t\xf4i s\u1EBD kh\xf4ng bao gi\u1EDD chia s\u1EBB ho\u1EB7c b\xe1n th\xf4ng tin khi kh\xf4ng c\xf3 s\u1EF1 \u0111\u1ED3ng \xfd c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content2:"Xem Ch\xednh s\xe1ch quy\u1EC1n ri\xeang t\u01B0 c\u1EE7a TikTok Shop \u0111\u1EC3 hi\u1EC3u c\xe1c quy\u1EC1n, ph\u01B0\u01A1ng ph\xe1p b\u1EA3o m\u1EADt d\u1EEF li\u1EC7u v\xe0 vi\u1EC7c s\u1EED d\u1EE5ng b\u1EA5t k\u1EF3 th\xf4ng tin n\xe0o c\u1EE7a b\u1EA1n.",tts_shop_purchase_protections_in_depth_data_privacy_content3:"C\u1EA7n tr\u1EE3 gi\xfap? Trung t\xe2m tr\u1EE3 gi\xfap \u1EA3o c\u1EE7a ch\xfang t\xf4i ho\u1EA1t \u0111\u1ED9ng 24/7 trong \u1EE9ng d\u1EE5ng TikTok v\xe0 nh\xe2n vi\xean tr\u1EF1c tuy\u1EBFn lu\x